We would love to hear from you!  Call us today at (647) 478-5422 so we can show you the difference an owner operated business can make!  Our reliable and professional Toronto movers and packers are here to help!

We're lovers of design, fine art and antiques.

Would you trust the people who move the Archibald Prize artworks with your precious antiques and heirlooms? Great, because that's us! Simply tell us when the move will cause the least amount of disruption to your home, office, gallery, store or your space, and we'll be there!

Our Vans & moving trucks are NEW, clean & fully equipped.
specialities:
Welcome to CARGO CABBIE®!

Let us take you on a little tour of our special services!  Cargo Cabbie provides high quality professional moving and packing services for all sizes and types of residential and commercial moves.  We also have a full-range of moving and packing supplies at our Box Shop that we can deliver straight to your door.
We help with all sizes of moves from Eight-bedroom houses to single-item deliveries (Cargo Cabbie Express).  We also provide in-home moves and on-site loading / unloading, if you are only looking to stage or rearrange your home, or move your furniture out to a pod / truck in your driveway.  We can help!  We also provide professional packing services if you would like help packing and/or unpacking your home or office.  You have the option of purchasing cardboard boxes or renting our eco-friendly plastic bins, whether we do the packing or you do.  Our crews are also skilled at furniture assembly / disassembly, if you have one or a few items you would like help with.  Whatever your moving or packing needs, we can help!

Visit our Box Shop online  We offer all sizes of boxes, bubble wrap, white newsprint, dish and glass kits, shrink wrap, tape, tape dispensers, art/mirror boxes, TV boxes and more!  If you are local to us in the downtown core of Toronto we can deliver your order free of charge.  

We look forward to hearing from you!  We're here to help!

profile:
WE  PROVIDE   FREE   ON   SITE   ESTIMATES IN THE GTA! 
 
WE PROVIDE TEMP CONTROLLED, SECURE STORAGE, ON MONTH TO MONTH BASES! CUSTOMERS THAT STORE THREE OR MORE MONTHS GET ONE MONTH FREE!!!
WE SELL BOXES, PACKING PAPER, MATTRESS BAGS, BUBBLE WRAP AND MUCH MORE! 
 
At Augusta Movers Toronto Inc., we understand the challenges when it comes to moving whether it is down the street or across the city. Moving your home or business to a new location is exciting but it can be stressful so let Augusta Movers take care of your moving needs and alleviate your anxiety. 
 
Augusta Movers offers a full range of moving, packing and storage solutions to fit your move and budget considerations including discounts for students and seniors. Our expertise in residential and commercial moving, packing and storage has earned us a solid reputation with our customers enabling our business to prosper from repeat business and referrals for local and long distance relocation. Our superior service and attention to all your moving requirements and details, makes us the best choice for your move. 
 
We are experts in what we do from smaller moves, packing and storage for apartment and condo dwellers to houses and commercial relocations of offices, stores, and restaurants. Our unique control and monitoring moving process allows our trained team of professional packers and movers to execute your move hassle-free – we guarantee it.  We believe direct communication is the key to a successful move; we will meet with you to discuss your moving requirements and provide you with a written estimate of the required services with no surprises. 
 
At Augusta Movers Toronto, we are dedicated to providing our customers with quality and fast service at competitive rates.  We are committed to consistently providing excellence in customer service unmatched and beyond industry standards; we will be there for you offering guidance and support from the beginning of your move from packing and storage to transportation of your belongings to your new location. 
 
We encourage you to browse around our site for more information on our moving, packingand storage services. To request a free estimate on your next residential and commercial move, call Augusta Movers Toronto at 416 665 9996.

profile:
Since 1992, Miracle Movers Toronto has provided thousands of satisfied customers with customized, comprehensive moving services across the GTA and Canada. Whether you're one person moving into a bachelor apartment or a midsize company moving 100 employees into a new office, our experienced, enthusiastic staff is ready to help you out.

In addition to providing basic transportation services, we can visit your home or office before the big day to plan the most efficient move possible, create a floor plan of your new destination so that you know precisely where your items will go, and even help pack - or provide boxes, padding and plastic wrap if you'd rather do so yourself. With satellite offices across Canada and partners around the world, we can then accommodate moves of any distancccommodate moves of any distance to any destination, including the USA.

At Miracle Movers Toronto, we pride ourselves on providing outstanding customer service: more than 80% of our customers are from referrals! Call us for free advice and quotations today!

profile:
Welcome to Viktoria Professional Movers – a company where customer care and satisfaction are our top priorities. 
 
There's no doubt about it, moving can be stressful!   Choosing responsible and experienced movers is one of the ways to alleviate that stress. When choosing a moving & storage company price is important, however the level of service your moving company provides you with is even more important, and often times cheap moving companies can end up costing you a fortune! Unfortunately, our industry abounds with companies whose aim to book as many jobs as they can by whatever means necessary. Many "lowball" estimates quickly balloon with unexpected charges while hurried workers provide disappointing service. For many of these companies protecting your property and ensuring your satisfaction is last on their list of priorities.
 
At Viktoria Professional Movers it's not about the number of moves, it's about the number of customers we leave happy & satisfied. Moving doesn't have to be complicated. Let us walk you through the process and get you on the way to a stress-free move to your new home. The key to a successful move is organization and we are the experts.
 
Whether you require moving, packing, or self-storage, you will never be just another client to us. Ever.

profile:
The goal at GetMovers is to provide detail-oriented moving assistance that's tailored to the needs of each customer.

That is why all GetMovers employees from call centre assistants to drivers get special trainings and their salary is highly affected by our customers satisfaction.

Our quality management system is adapting quickly to client’s needs, saving you time and money.

So, if you want to move your belongings stress-free, on time and in full safety GetMovers is the company to turn to.

We are specializing on local residential and commercial moving. Moving can be very stressful and complicated if you haven’t chosen the right moving company and completed all the preparations needed, ahead of your moving day.
You should be checking if the company have full insurance coverage for your content and the properties, full equipment including packaging materials and tools to assemble and dissemble your furniture, how many years they are in business and read their third party reviews and must have back up trucks just in case something happen on your moving date! Our Team will be happy to advice you on other things that are extremely important during your move, so call us today and will be gladly assisting you.


Moving process starts with packing.

Packing is really time consuming.

Do you know that a 2-bedroom apartment will typically take a homeowner or renter 6 hours – 1 day to pack. A two-bedroom home will likely take up to 2 days

Our trained GetMovers team is happy to free you several precious hours.

We know how to handle bulky, fragile, oddly shaped and unique items to prevent damage while transportation.
We use high quality packing supplies, containers, wardrobe boxes to ensure the smoothness of moving process.

If you prefer packing by yourself, we can deliver all necessary packing materials to your doorstep.

We also provide Partial Packing Service. It means that we would pack or unpack only large items or pack up items in a specific room.

The decision is always yours.

Get in touch and we'll Pack and unpack It for You.



Getmovers has a large operating network across Canada. So, if you. need to relocate from Toronto to Vancouver or from Edmonton to Calgary we are happy to help you.

We’re not just moving experts, we’re relocation experts. Since 2008 we constantly enriching our expertise moving people and businesses around Canada.

We have the knowledge you need for a successful relocation.

We've partnered with competent international moving companies near you to help you ship your goods to any country in the world.

You can delegate us the whole process or the most time-consuming tasks while relocation.


Get your quote on get movers.ca


Looking for secure and climate control storage space with full access to? With over 10,000 Sqft   storage capacity GetMovers provides secure solutions for short or long-term storage.

Whether you need to store furniture, commercial goods or professional equipment, our secure storage facilities across Canada are equipped with the best technology to keep your belongings safe.

Our storage facilities are regularly inspected and well equipped, we make sure your belongings are securely stored in the best conditions.

Get Movers offers both private and corporate relocation services.

A well-designed action plan of your office relocation would minimize the loss of productivity for your business.

GetMovers are well trained to pack and move your company’s assets such as office furniture and electronics to your new premises.

You probably would ask yourself after everything we covered here is why should I be choosing Get Movers? Here are only the few reasons why:
1.	All our movers are professionals and  exceptionally well trained.
2.	We use the latest technology solution to monitor live the process of your move, we know where our trucks are, crews located and their live actions (use Samsara) so while calling our customer service team will be able to answer all your questions live!
3.	Full customer service, support and management team is here to serve you 7 days a week!
4.	Back up trucks and crews in cases for last minute moves or emergencies 
5.	Exceptionally high referral rate based on our past customers that are referring us.
6.	Honest upfront pricing without any hidden fees or surprises after
7.	We are One stop shop for all your moving needs.
8.	Nationwide Canadian coverage allowing us serving you anywhere in Canada and US.
9.	Great Team with Over 12 years of successful experience in the moving industry.



So, call us now at 1888 to get your move arranged or Get your free quote on get movers.ca

Get Movers – Caring while Carrying

Our priority is to make sure that all the possessions of our clients, which are filled with spiritual significance will bring the same joy throughout time, no matter how many times they are being moved to new houses, and our basic goal is to make sure that our clients remember us only from positive experience and perspective.

Make your move easier by using Frogbox eco-friendly reusable moving boxes and other moving supplies. We have worked with all the Movers in the cities we service and can refer credible movers (and tell you who to avoid :)).  
FROGBOX was a successful contender on The Dragon's Den.

profile:
Rockbrune Brothers Ltd is a long time family run business. 

Ajax Local Moving
   We understand that even a local move in Ajax can be stressful. That's why we want to take the pressure off of you and deal with all the small 
   details. Its time you got an affordable move option in Ajax.
~~~
Long Distance Moving
   When you're moving long distance from or to Ajax, our main goal is to give you a peace of mind knowing your belonging will arrive safely. 
   We have expert movers that will carry out the entire move process seamlessly and give you the best service.
~~~
International Moving
   We are proficient in completing international moves from the start to finish. We are knowledgeable in the customs, rules, and guidelines for 
   international moving. We will also ensure your belongings are kept safe throughout the journey.
~~~
Office Moving
   If you're moving your office in the Ajax area we offer affordable rates for your commercial needs. Our main priority for office moves is to 
   minimise the downtime for your business so we will get everything done with as little disruption as possible.
~~~
Moving Services
   We offer service for all of the Durham region including Ajax, Oshawa, Whitby, Markham and Pickering!
   - Need Packing? We Can Do the Packing For You!
   - Free In-house Estimates. We Guarantee Our Rates!
   - Dedicated Moving Coordinator to Help You During Your Moving Journey; All Our Staff Are Bonded.
   - Professional Movers Since 1920
   - We Have the Right Equipment to Move All Size Homes; Studios, Condos & Houses.
   - Safe & Secure Protection Options For Your Move.
~~~
~~~

Our History: 
      As well known movers today, the story of the Rockbrune Brothers began in the 1920’s.Farming was a tough way to make a living. This 
   way of life was even more difficult for a young man with dreams of someday getting off the farm. Robert Rockbrune was a restless 
   teenager working on his families land just outside Perth, Ontario. One day he packed up what little belongings he had and headed to a 
   job in Oshawa, a city that was booming in the automotive industry. As the 20’s came to a close, Robert met Robina, who soon became his 
   wife. In the years ahead, he and Robina started a family, eventually having seven children, two daughters and five sons - “Mom and Dad 
   were pretty resourceful”, he says. “You had to be back then. It was not a time to live, it was a time to survive.” They hauled hay for 
   farmers, goods from the CP railway and whatever else they could. As word spread about City Cartage, the company grew. Towards the end 
   of the 40’s and into the 50’s the post war boom saw a huge growth in business so, they added more trucks. They also received 
   permission from the government for moving goods outside of the Oshawa area. They charged $2.00 an hour, which was enough to pay the 
   bills and their staff.
      As the sons grew older, they joined the family business. Today three of them, Robert, William, and Joseph, still run the company. 
   Six of Robert and Robina’s grandchildren also help lead Rockbrune Bros. Movers and their offices in Oshawa, Ajax, Newmarket, and 
   Barrie into the next generation.

profile:
Benini Moving and Storage is a Toronto-based relocation and storage company. Our mission is to provide our clients with the highest quality of service, founded upon the principles of efficiency and reliability. We offer a wide variety of MOVING SERVICES, carefully customized to meet the needs and budget of each client.

To start off, get a FREE ESTIMATE for your move. One of our professional moving managers will contact you with your quote, and answer all your questions. We will even provide you with FREE DELIVERY of all the packing supplies you need.

With Benini, you can relax knowing that your valuables will be handled with the utmost care.
products:
WHAT WE DO

1/ We sign a contract before the job starts with the starting time indicated and the conditions were already discussed with the customer.
2/ We completely wrap the furniture with thick moving blankets to avoid any damages or scratches.
3/ We carefully pack the dishes, glasses and other fragile items with white packing paper.
4/ We take care of pictures and paintings.
5/ We load the truck in a proper way to avoid the furniture shifting and damaging during transportation.
6/We try finding creative solutions to the issues which may occur during the job.
7/ We hoist sofas and other heavy pieces through a balcony if there is no other ways to bring them in.
8/ We conduct our service in a very friendly manner.
9/We work very hard until the job is completed.
services:
WHAT WE DO NOT DO:

1/ We are never late. In fact, we always try to arrive early. 
2/ We do not have “stair” charges.
3/ We do not have ANY hidden charges.
4/ We do not prolong the job deliberately in order to make extra money.
5/ We do not keep our customers’ belongings locked in the truck as a “hostage” while negotiating to get extra payment.
6/ We do not insist to get paid in full before the job is completed.
7/ We do not insist to receive free pizza and beer for lunch.
8/ We do not insist to be tipped even if you are not pleased of our service.

 We always give written estimates whether it’s a flat price or an hourly price. All our in-house estimates are free of cost.

 Our staff is extremely professional with an experience of more than 10 years. They know what they’re doing.

COVID UPDATE:
 We're doing our best to ensure the safety of our clients as well as our front-line crew members during this tough time:
 Our trucks are washed and sanitized periodically.
 All personal protective equipment including gloves and masks is mandatory for every crew member.
 As for the safety of our clients and crew members, we ask all our clients to avoid more than 2 people while moving and to maintain 2 m distance.

services:
Local Movers​
To offer the best moving home services, Coraza Movers has staff members with a host of skills in electrical installations, carpentry, plumbing and house-keeping. We invest in training to ensure the staff are equipped with emerging trends in the moving industry.

We provide all the necessary packing materials to ensure no damages to your furniture. Our vehicles are custom built for carrying items that need care and safety, they are padded on the inside to minimize damage, and they have lashing rails for tying and fastening the items.

Long Distance Movers
A majority of our moves are done for the local area’s residents, we also can work long distances too, when you ask us to!

Office Movers
When relocating your office take advantage of Coraza Movers vast experience, professional advice and meticulous execution to ensure minimal downtime. We are adept in moving large organizations where project management and coordination across departments is required to ensure a chaos-free and disrupted move. Our movers ensure your valuable files, computers and furniture are handled with maximum integrity. We are able to undertake moves under all weather conditions.

Our Office Moving Services guarantees you the following;

Pre-packing of files before the actual move.
Labeling of various departments before the move.
Free mounting TVs and various wall hangings.
Connection of various electronic appliances e.g. computers and printers.
Allocation of trucks with tail lifts for easier loading of heavy goods.
Provision of hydraulic trolleys for handling and movement of heavy items such as safes.
Disassembly and reassembly of bulk filers.

profile:
Vaultra Storage is a 100% Canadian owned and operated. The company is a one-stop storage solution, featuring self storage, pick up and delivery service, LAUFT coworking spaces and rental moving boxes. Each facility offers simple, seamless and secure storage solutions for all. Whether looking to store for business or personal use, Vaultra’s team will find the services that fit their customers best.

Vaultra self storage facilities offer convenient and secure locations, with units that range from traditional drive-up, indoor, heated, climate controlled to outdoor vehicle storage. Visit vaultrastorage.ca/self-storage to find a location nearby!

The pick up and delivery service, Vaultra Door to Door, is available throughout the GTA. It's simple: Vaultra movers pick up items and store them at a Vaultra facility. When the items are needed again, Vaultra Door to Door returns them! To see service areas, as well as the Door to Door storage plans available, visit d2d.vaultra.ca.

LAUFT coworking spaces are featured in Vaultra Storage's Toronto Castlefield and Ajax locations. Their state of the art facilities are perfect for business owners and/or entrepreneurs who want a space to work, while having their inventory right around the corner. Book a coworking space at lauft.work!

The rental moving box service, Vaultra CityBoxes, offers 27” x 17” x 12” bins that are stackable and reusable. First Vaultra CityBoxes delivers the bins. Then, clients pack, move and unpack. Afterwards, they pick up the bins! To see the service area and rent moving boxes, visit vaultrastorage.ca/bin-rental.

profile:
IMPORTANT TO KNOW
- We always provide  written estimates that can be completed either in your home or over the phone, whichever is best for you. All estimates are free of cost.
- We do not surprise you with hidden charges at the time of final payment.
- We provide top notch service at reasonable prices

Why Should you feel comfortable in selecting us?
The processes we follow ensure you will receive a consistent result designed to exceed your expectations, reduce your stress levels and deliver you a happy comfortable experience.
Through our services we provide you tailor made solutions based on your needs, not out of the box offered to everyone.
We are local and family run, readily available to help you.
Our people are trained in a way that ensures you feel secure knowing your belongings are treated like they are our own.

QUESTIONS YOU SHOULD ASK EVERY COMPANY
1) Who Are You?
- We are a locally owned and operated family run business based in Mississauga, Ontario.   We are not your typical moving, storage or junk removal company.  We are a unique “One Stop ” solution for home owners and businesses.   We created Space Makers to help our clients run their lives and businesses with less stress and more comfort through less clutter.
We are “The simple solution to your Home’s (or businesses) evolution”

2) What Services Do You Offer?
- We offer the following:
Local moving – we pad, wrap and protect your belongings like they were our own.
Storage – we will remove and store items you do not need right now but may need in the future.
Junk – we will remove items you no longer need.
Donation or Auction – we will remove items you no longer need but do not want to see go to waste.
In home moving – for staging or simply rearranging, let us do the heavy lifting for you

3) What Do You Believe and why do you do what you do?
- We believe that no two client situations are the same.
- We believe that clients desire a “one stop” solution for their space making needs rather than dealing with numerous different service -providers.
- We believe that by properly analyzing the needs of our clients through client friendly conversation we will accurately understand their specific objectives.
- We believe that our clients deserve customized solutions with transparent quotes based on their specific objectives.
- We believe that by delivering quality and on-going training for all of our employees we will be an employer of choice for professional and personable employees.
- We believe that by having well-trained, professional and personable employees deliver a customized solution based on our understanding of our client’s objectives, we will be the “gold standard” for residential and commercial moving and storage.

4) Who do you work with?
- Our clients are just like you. We work with residential home-owners and renters to assist them with their local moves and with space-creation needs within their homes. 
- We also work with Business clients helping them with their moving and storage requirements.

5) What makes you different?
A) Our company
- Unique, not your average moving, storage or junk removal company.
- Local
- the simple solution to your home or business’s evolution.

B) Our Solutions
- Unique – tailored to your needs.
- Diverse, one stop company to reduce stress, save you time and money.
- Consistent, reliable, we follow our processes in every step.

C) Our People
- Well trained, professional and personable.
- Family run. We treat you and our team like they are our family - they are!
- Integrity, we were founded based on our core business beliefs including transparency and honesty.

profile:
We are a group of professional individuals who have been working in the moving industry for many years, taking our experience from small-scale businesses to large-scale businesses, from all across Canada. We have been working with many companies and know the ins- and outs of the industry, the stars and the bad apples.  This experience has allowed us to shape our approach to moving and to develop enhanced moving techniques that allow us to offer you the most effective move possible. Our vision is to change the negative association made to the moving industry and show our clients just who we are: professional, experienced, friendly, reliable, and honest movers. We work hard to ease what is historically known as a stressful day: moving. Our teams work effortlessly to complete our valued clients’ move to their satisfaction and not leave until our client is completely satisfied. 
 
We are not just a team of movers, we are a family working together and supporting each other to bring out the best of who we are and to project that quality into your move. Working as a family allows us to bring a more personal touch to your move, treating your belongings as if they were our own. We understand that every move is unique, thus they each have a different set of needs and requirements that our family is able to address by attentively listening to our clients. Indeed, we treat every move with the same professionalism but every move is tailored and personalized to match your needs. Our reputation is through word of mouth, so whether you are using our moving services, packing services or any other services, we will always ensure to go above and beyond your expectations. We promise that with The Six Movers Inc., you will get the care you are looking for, from our family to yours.

profile:
OUT OF BUSINESS Duties and responsibilities for your furniture movers: 1. The movers will greet our customers 2. Cover floors and woodwork in the home to protect them from damage. 3. Determine special packing and wrapping requirements for items such as electronic, antiques, beds and appliances 4. Wrap all wooden items with blankets and all upholstered items with plastic making sure that everything is secure for transit 5. Courteously but briefly answer customers' questions or refer questions to office staff 6. Determine the order in which to load furniture to ensure that bulky or heavy items are placed in the lower part of the truck box or moving van 7. Work with a partner or use dollies or straps to move very heavy items such as appliances and large pieces of furniture 8. Arrange articles in tiers to form a compact load, using padding and straps to secure articles and prevent shifting when the truck is in motion 9. Complete a walk around inspection with the customer to ensure that all items have been loaded 10. The driver will drive our moving truck to your final destination 11. Lay out floor runners and determine where items should be placed at destination point 12. Remove straps and padding from articles and unload the truck 13. Reassemble furniture pieces that were disassembled for the move 14. Clean up and make sure everything has been delivered in the same condition as it was when it was picked up 15. Have our customer sign the bill of lading (contract) and collect payment in full ************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************ Characteristics of our movers: 1. Physical strength, stamina and co-ordination 2. The ability to follow written and spoken instructions 3. The ability to judge distances and space 4. The ability to work independently 5. The ability to organize their work and time effectively 6. The ability to get along with customers who are often under stress 7. Work co-operatively with fellow employees 8. Have a neat appearance


************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************

products: We sell a full line of NEW Moving supplies.  Delivery for moving supplies for our customers is FREE.
services:
We offer a very unique service to all our customers.  On the day of your move, our movers will show up at your door dressed in uniform and with our very clean, well-equipped truck to the job done in a professional and timely manner.  We offer what people on the day of their move are looking for.....care, professionalism and quality.

On the day of your move, you are entitled to the following items FREE:
1.  Wardrobes

2.  Plastic for upholstered items

3.  Floor runners

4.  Quilted moving blankets

5.  Bannister covers (where required)

6.  Full disassembly and reassembly (where required)

All trucks are equipped with a generous supply of moving blankets, plastics and dollies.  We cover all furniture with moving blankets and all upholstered items including mattresses will be covered in plastic for FREE!!  We have different size of trucks to suit all your moving needs.


Local moving charges are based on hourly rates.  The rate begins when the crew arrives at your first location and covers the total time of the move: the loading, driving to the new location and the unloading.  Additional stops in between locations are included in the total moving time.  There are no extra charges for multiple stops.


In addition to the hourly rate, there is a one time fee called travel time.  This charge covers the mover's cost for traveling from their facility to your location and back to their office once the move is complete.  This charge is at the same rate as the hourly fee.                                                           


******************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************

profile:
Lewis Abbeywood Moving & Storage specializes in a full range of moving services including local & long-distance moving, packing, storage and commercial moves. We understand that moving can be stressful -- it is our mission to make your move as smooth and hassle-free as possible. 

Whether you are a corporation moving your entire staff to a new location, a business needing to move your equipment without missing a day in operation, an individual embarking on a complex international move, or just a family moving into your new home – you're all looking for a moving company you can rely on. Lewis Abbeywood Moving & Storage Inc. provides a complete moving solution to both residents and businesses, and is a reliable Toronto mover you can trust.

Our business started as a local family owned Toronto moving company-- now, we service all of Canada, the United States and beyond. At Lewis Abbeywood Moving & Storage Inc. we have been helping all kinds of people and businesses, in as many different situations as you can imagine, get their belongings to places near and far, and we have been doing it for over 4 decades. That's a lot of moves! Through our long history we have learned that one thing is important to you above all else: Trust.

Call us today for a quote!

We pride ourselves on being one of the few owner-operated moving companies servicing the GTA, Southern Ontario, and across Canada. Established in 2013, we work hard to ensure every client's needs are satisfied.  

When you book a service with Maple Rose Movers, you’re not just getting untrained labourers and a vehicle; we contract regular, trained staff to perform each move, delivery, collection, pack, or de-clutter. Believe it or not, moving furniture is not as simple as it seems. What could be worse than moving into a new space only to be left with dented walls or damaged furniture or a huge bill?

A bit of a strange approach to moving, perhaps? Our philosophy is to give you a great move at an affordable price during a stressful time. And we hope you tell everyone about us! A referral is the highest compliment a business can ever receive. 

We strive each day to make sure that our clients are happy; our philosophy is working and we owe it all to you, our valued clients.

As the Moving Industry is unregulated, only allow a REPUTABLE corporation that is insured to move your belongings safely and professionally at an affordable rate. When it comes to hiring home service providers, never go for those who advertise to be the cheapest.
As cheap often means cutting corners. Always make sure you select a service provider with great reviews and reputation - after all, they'll be in your home, near your valuables and in your family.


WHY YOU SHOULD CHOOSE WRAP AND MOVE INC.?
Moving can be difficult, stressful and back-breaking work, so allow us to do the heavy lifting and relieve some hassle for you!! We provide reliable, professional and affordable moving solutions for all of your moving needs - big or small!!
Our expert movers will transport your belongings in an efficient and timely manner to ensure the best care is taken of your things Each truck comes standard with floor runners, quilted moving blankets, plastic wrap, dollies and specialized straps for moving large/heavy items such as fridges and washing machines.

✅Among Top 1% Moving Companies.

Our trained Movers are proficient in moving all your belongings. We carefully and expertly pack everything in our truck so all your valuables are safe. 

Need help organizing and packing?
We are pro in that that too. We are highly experienced, motivated and passionate in packaging, unpacking, assembling and disassembling all types of items from appliances and furniture to clothing. Your items will reach your destination in perfect condition and with utmost ease of accessibility.
Available for moving in the Greater Toronto Area and surrounding areas 24/7.

profile:
Our goal is to provide the highest quality of service possible and to continue solidifying our reputation as a premier moving and storage company. Sokol Moving Inc specializes in local and long distance moving as well as residential and commercial moves. In addition to our moving services, we provide packing services, secured storage and a variety of moving supplies. Are you making a move? You can count on Sokol Moving Inc as we will be there from start to finish. Join our many satisfied customers and see why Sokol Moving Inc is the leading moving and storage company.


Our Mission Statement

To express our integrity, work ethic and attitude by always doing the right thing, by outworking our competitors, by choosing a positive attitude and to foster a family environment. In short, do whatever it takes to meet the needs of our customers. Beginning with our in home estimate till the moment we place the last piece of furniture in your new home, our company will change the way you look at movers. We take the time to anticipate your needs, come to the job prepared, and stay until our clients are completely satisfied.

Sokol Moving has helped families move for many years.

In all that time, we have learned what it takes to ensure the smoothest possible transition for you, and your valued possessions. In fact, we treat your possessions as if they were our own... from hand-packing every piece of crystal, to double-padding your fine woods and personal equipment. Our movers are specially trained in safety and handling procedures for your unique and fragile items.

Sokol Moving also protects your peace of mind by consulting with you first on the issues that concern you most. We will offer you our professional consultation about the most cost effective strategies for you, and maintain accurate and complete checklists at all times. We can even provide storage for those items that you may not want to move immediately.

Your move with Sokol Moving will not only be trouble-free, but also punctual. We use well-planned communication systems to track the locations of our vans and adhere to strict delivery schedules. When you arrive at your new home, Sokol Moving will be ready to unload your possessions and get you settled right in. By practicing respect for you and what is yours, Sokol Moving has earned the trust of families locally and abroad.

Contact us today to provide a quote for your big day!

profile: When it comes to relocation, finding a reliable mover (Toronto moving services, Calgary moving services, Halifax, Regina etc.) with a trustworthy reputation is critical. Unfortunately, the advancements of the Internet have made it easy for anyone to put up a nice looking website and pose as a professional movers. Though the appearance may be professional, some of these moving services are actually unprofessional operators who may not even own a truck, or have access to proper moving equipment. To give consumers peace of mind when looking for a good movers, the Canadian Moving and Storage Network (CMSN) established their own Movers & Storage Search System which certifies that moving and storage members have not only agreed to abide by our high standards and ethics, but have also passed a thorough services background check. The CMSN's new Movers & Storage Search System makes it easy for consumers to find qualified movers by company name, mover type, province, town, postal code, and many other useful search criteria.

profile:
Welcome to G2G Fitness Solutions. When you purchase new equipment or need something moved, two thoughts that come to mind are: Can I trust someone with my equipment and what will my investment be with such an endeavor?  With so much already on your plate from researching for the perfect machine or moving in to your new home we want to make this easy on you. With our experience in this industry and emphasis on positive customer service we want to put your mind at ease. Keep reading to learn more, and reach out with questions on what we have to offer.

*****

We will move all of your fitness equipment. First we will test each piece to see what condition it is in. Then we will dismantle and make sure all pieces are protected from the move. We also use moving blankets to protect all areas of your property. Staying safe and protecting floors and walls are important to you and it is important to us as well.  We will then transport, move, assemble and test each piece of equipment to ensure that it's ready to be used.

*****

Delivery and Installation:
Did you just purchase a new machine? We can deliver it from the retailer to your home. If desired we can also install and test the machine so that you can start on your path to hitting your fitness goals.

*****
​
Dismantle:
We can prepare your fitness equipment for the move by breaking it down and protecting it. If needed we can come back to assemble your equipment.

*****

Give us a call today.
name: G2 G Fitness Solutions
